name: Midnight Sun
description:
I will introduce my next series called 'The Point of No Return'. This photo was 1st series, The Point of No Return also be my photography exhibition which will be held on December 12th 2021.

I dig a research at Porong, Sidoarjo, East Java for every week in a month on last September. Mud Volcano, the disaster from year to year has no end, which triggered me to going there to capture all what's left on there.

More series to come.

Fujifilm X-T20 with Fujinon XF Lens 35mm F2.
5923 x 3948 px, JPEG.
